# Tauri
# Rust build output / generated capability schemas (also covered locally in
# apps/desktop/src-tauri/.gitignore; kept here as a safety net).
apps/desktop/src-tauri/target
apps/desktop/src-tauri/gen/schemas
# Tauri updater signing keys — the private key must NEVER be committed (it lives
# in CI secrets). The .pub is public, but ignore both to be safe.
*.key
*.key.pub
